tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T17:46:03.000Z","msg":"你都識話提子對貓係劇毒<br />\n我屌你老母你食撚左山埃你會唔會唔撚睇醫生係屋企打下飛機先呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5590cf7a19f40fa7001f10b30935046aa7b296b2","tid":782334,"uid":12158,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T17:46:31.000Z","msg":"帶啦！洗少少錢保住你家人條命有咩所謂？佢世界只有你咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e79d71e0423305ad97305b9a1392f1615b8d525","tid":782334,"uid":96070,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T17:46:33.000Z","msg":"隻貓有你呢個主人真係慘"},{"pid":"2a52725eb46aed75cd95067b1fb771fa459c8285","tid":782334,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T17:59:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1af30dfd7eed2ec3c3587ebb34a1a39055e51e","tid":782334,"uid":59669,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T18:01:56.000Z","msg":"其實冇科學證明貓唔食得提子<br />\n啲人覺得唔食得係因為狗食咗會腎衰竭<br />\n不過最好都係唔好比貓食啦<br />\n留意吓有冇唔舒服，作嘔"},{"pid":"729fe25bce8ff8fc3671a5993b9e67c98e317258","tid":782334,"uid":162689,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T18:09:54.000Z","msg":"其實提子係對狗劇毒，有D狗狗食少少都可以好大件事<br />\n相比起狗，貓貓因為食提子而岀事嘅report就少好多，當然每隻貓嘅reaction都唔同<br />\n建議樓主可以monitor，睇下貓貓有冇不適，例如嘔或肚瀉。<br />\n最緊要都係睇有冇喝水同尿尿，因為提子有可能引至急性腎衰竭<br />\n擔心嘅話，可以去睇emergency，佢哋多數會用藥去令貓貓嘔，但貓貓可能已經吸收左。"},{"pid":"7758d2d5167f5c3a89cad598b42cf3bc559882bf","tid":782334,"uid":179348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4e79d71e0423305ad97305b9a1392f1615b8d525","tid":782334,"uid":96070,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T17:46:33.000Z","msg":"隻貓有你呢個主人真係慘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T18:18:06.000Z","msg":"真係<br />\n連帶隻貓去檢查嘅錢都想慳 真係好撚仆街"},{"pid":"c43b8bad67dd9bade3cb1c02998718772b925840","tid":782334,"uid":84032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7758d2d5167f5c3a89cad598b42cf3bc559882bf","